data.description: Welcome to this Thriving neighborhood! Close to shopping ,restaurants , and Fort Liberty. Step into this 3 bedroom 2 bath gem! Boasting over 1200 square feet of comfortable living space. Step into a freshly painted interior and Re-finished hardwood floors making this home a fresh comfortable atmosphere. Brand New upgraded stainless Steel refrigerator and updated kitchen makes this kitchen ready for you and your family. Laundry room is conveniently located off of the kitchen. Very private Backyard fenced in! Exterior was recently pressure washed providing this home with a fresh clean look. Roof was replaced in 2016 with upgraded architectural shingles. Don't miss your chance to make this home yours call today for a private showing!!
